paragraph: You work hard enough to need a presence on the web. Staggerlee Development is about respecting that, and working hard enough to get out of the way of your goals. Let's approach this project not only with a respect for who you are, but what your time means. The internet may be a new hat for you, but it's still your hat. Let's get you back to wearing it!
linkHeader: Reasonable pricing, let's start a consultation. »
